model.dataType.tempData
Class FriendTempData

java.lang.Object
  model.dataType.tempData.FriendTempData

public class FriendTempData
extends Object

Holds partial UserData objects for use in transferring from the database to other locations. This is the raw data that should be stored in the database. All other data about a user should be fetched from the server.
